Is there an assertNotEquals()...

Having just written the following test ( to confirm/disprove   a possible
bug with a hash code generation code) I saw that there is

assertSame()
assertNotSame()

assertTrue()
assertFalse()

assertEquals()

but no
assertNotEquals()

which means I have to do: assertFalse((obj1.equals(obj2)));

I know its not a big deal, I just feel assertEquals is missing its expected
pair.

Andy
